{"tid":416692,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2017 日本國民好感度最佳女星 Top 10","createTime":"2017-09-28T03:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T03:17:53.000Z","uid":60286,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c74f383b2816a50c7667f4fc60fd66d7ef1eaa33","tid":416692,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/112122_59664bd3fc5a40351b835c6a9853f32d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F112122_59664bd3fc5a40351b835c6a9853f32d.jpg&h=f708bdd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應成為日本國民度好感藝人，不只要本身就是時下炙手可熱的一線明星，同時還要在言行上廣受日本民眾喜愛，即使像廣瀨鈴這位當紅的日本美少女，在日本網友評論中卻依然以負面印象居多，日本 Video Research 就針對 2017 年度好感度最佳女星排出 Top 10 ，以下這些女星才是真是的火紅名人。<br />\n<br />\n第 10 名、北川景子。<br />\n<br />\n日劇中以獨立、強勢女性角色聞名的北川景子，在與 Daigo 結婚之後可以說是日本人最欽羨的模範夫妻之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/113227_9cfa231eb9013dc13b030b05dfcfaf9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F113227_9cfa231eb9013dc13b030b05dfcfaf9a.jpg&h=8b5f2152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 9 名、井本絢子。<br />\n<br />\n飛往各國拍攝節目《阿Q冒險中》的女性搞笑藝人。<br />\n<br />\n第 8 名、渡邊直美。<br />\n<br />\n台日混血兒渡邊直美可以說是難得一見的女諧星，她不只是當紅的搞笑藝人，同時也是許多人心目中的胖妹時尚教主。<br />\n<br />\n第 7 名、石原里美。<br />\n<br />\n近期剛出版最新個人寫真書的石原聰美，現在已經是可以與新垣結衣、綾瀨遙並列的日劇女王。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/113337_7c07b74b9f89064ce32a66541e93a05c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F113337_7c07b74b9f89064ce32a66541e93a05c.jpg&h=24de7256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/112250_73a91dc1fbadb15b0d7c6076145057ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F112250_73a91dc1fbadb15b0d7c6076145057ac.jpg&h=1f5ccb3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 6 名、深田恭子。<br />\n<br />\n永遠不過氣、永遠傻白田的深田恭子，以肉感的身材深深吸引男性粉絲之外，深田恭子是難得總是在日劇中裝可愛，卻依然獲得許多女性粉絲支持的美麗女星。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/112413_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F112413_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=f48953f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 5 名、DREAMS COME TRUE。<br />\n<br />\n日本國民性的音樂團體，DREAMS COME TRUE 擁有許多讓每個人都能夠朗朗上口的 hit曲。<br />\n<br />\n第 4 名、綾瀨遙。<br />\n<br />\n常年的好感度最佳女性藝人冠軍綾瀨遙，在今年的聲勢變得稍弱，不過她很快就要以日本電視台的新劇《太太，請小心輕放》美麗回歸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/112918_285a511615d5b7ad3b6f3fb1f83acc70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F112918_285a511615d5b7ad3b6f3fb1f83acc70.jpg&h=ea067c62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=0l2aN8lk3Sg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D2%26v%3D0l2aN8lk3Sg&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=253b6c04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=0l2aN8lk3Sg</a><br />\n<br />\n第 3 名、天海祐希。<br />\n<br />\n又美又獨立的女王，可以說是所有單身女性最理想的模範，看外表你絕對不敢相信天海祐希已經 50 歲了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/112639_b97f7fedc86815417e3c9f0de3546b17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F112639_b97f7fedc86815417e3c9f0de3546b17.jpg&h=89c2ee4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 2 名、淺田真央。<br />\n<br />\n今年 4 月宣布退役的日本花式滑冰女王，她與韓國選手金妍兒之間的愛恨情仇更是精彩。<br />\n<br />\n第 1 名、新垣結衣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年以《逃恥》成為年度話題女演員，在今年又演出觀眾期盼多年的《Code Blue》第三季，讓新垣結衣終於能夠打敗好感度女王綾瀨遙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/113105_2d34ce9723b7fd07427b8624deb07e7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F113105_2d34ce9723b7fd07427b8624deb07e7b.jpg&h=f4d3bba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/112745_0d7878deb18b7e0b0eabca5cf66f427d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F112745_0d7878deb18b7e0b0eabca5cf66f427d.jpg&h=47b30289&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74b8b99ace7d6bda762701c780c3556255b92065","tid":416692,"uid":69585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:37:40.000Z","msg":"結衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf91456b1fed4c6a9a6774004e847cc24b4e5ae","tid":416692,"uid":83342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:40:57.000Z","msg":"BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc862842f71f23074b7f64706049075d49ad1fd6","tid":416692,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"新垣結衣老公留名"},{"pid":"bb64f5298877b27c0305bb476e90c10bd3c9fe3e","tid":416692,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:00:25.000Z","msg":"女王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb50132822d610150550b614b47d2eea7c11d41","tid":416692,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"第10名都有圖<br />\n其他又會冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d710a260d3bab3cc9860f5413386a2c72ee7ce","tid":416692,"uid":129273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第10名都有圖<br />\n其他又會冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n渡邊直美唔洗圖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6032fe721b84300809d72f169ccefc2bceff48","tid":416692,"uid":128119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:43:57.000Z","msg":"冇長澤雅美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1613f1b82161e2e434fd717b98af0e5e4cd3768c","tid":416692,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:59:57.000Z","msg":"有幾個無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b024d4a349b0d8c990bcad9b1d491696fad0ffb","tid":416692,"uid":28068,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:24:24.000Z","msg":"諗住入黎睇朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3d27c19a0203fbea83121a07b1c283565ec77c","tid":416692,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:27:12.000Z","msg":"女王的教室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120890479c97113da282f8488620186c3eebbc25","tid":416692,"uid":4180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T09:04:43.000Z","msg":"肥恭三十幾歲都仲係咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但點解個淺田真央會咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b50276456e222d5fc347be32fde45673bf5ae8","tid":416692,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T09:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住入黎睇朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望一望點知原來唔係若有若無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642f5e879a5f8e3a3e4bb26a638bd0fdee7fd0bb","tid":416692,"uid":1975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T09:05:29.000Z","msg":"麻友g呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd4dd468f10e233c9776fabe262150952dbb10a","tid":416692,